    Disciplinary Action: Format

        This window should be able to capture any disciplinary action taken on a particular staff.

The field should be Emp. ID, [Name, Place at present & Category (should be auto filled based on EMP ID selected)]

        Description of the disciplinary action taken
        Level of Corrective Action taken (option to select one)

Verbal Warning/ Counseling

Written warning

Suspension       

Termination

Comments if any

Option to search the Disciplinary Action data for any specific EMP id or Name.